data.description: This is it if you are looking for a next generational living layout. A large 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. A very comfortable home with 2 bedrooms and 1 bath on one side and large 2 bedrooms and 2 baths on the other side.  Property features 2 family rooms and a laundry room that could be a fifth bedroom.   The property features a brand-new roof, A side driveway for 3-4 cars or boat.    Enter the back yard and you will find a tropical oasis that features a free form pool and tropical landscaping.  This property also features natural gas for an outdoor kitchen. All offers considered.
